Init creates the .newton workspace layout, installs the Newton template with aikit-sdk, and writes default configs so you can run immediately.

Usage: newton init [OPTIONS] [PATH]

Arguments:
  [PATH]
          Location to initialize (defaults to current directory)

Options:
      --template-source <SOURCE>
          Template source passed to aikit-sdk (owner/repo, URL, or local path)

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')

Example:
    newton init ./workspace
